1 A BILL FOR AN ACT relating to public health and welfare; to amend
2 sections 71-6038 and 71-6039, Reissue Revised Statutes of Nebraska;
3 to provide for employment of nurse aides in intellectual and
4 developmental disability facilities; and to repeal the original
5 sections.
6 Be it enacted by the people of the State of Nebraska,
